{"tid":485782,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新北驚見「雨衣裸女」　三點全露路人嚇傻:P","createTime":"2017-12-01T08:59:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-01T11:43:31.000Z","uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"54c5106914ad2cc1533f19bb97eadad7db3e47d2","tid":485782,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T08:59:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n昨日北台灣下雨一整天，有網友疑似在新北市永福停車場附近，驚見一名只穿件黃色透明雨衣以及白鞋的裸女，由於雨衣透明，女子又全身赤裸，隨著強風豪雨，整件雨衣緊貼身體肌膚，照片中可以清楚看到胸前兩點以及身體曲線，讓該網友驚呼「真的不要不相信世上有鬼這種事，就在剛剛我真的遇到了...」，並把2張照片PO上網路，還標註「本土無碼」「一件雨衣走天下」「有夠狂」。<br />\n<br />\n照片被轉載至臉書專頁《爆料公社》引發網友熱烈討論，有網友留言「太猛了..今天她最美..」「最新款的時尚薄紗～」「國王的雨衣」「媽媽咪呀」「內衣內褲都沒穿 誇張」「還記得穿鞋耶...」「我看了什麼」（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171201/640_31b64b395307898245a652a33d23ca76.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171201%2F640_31b64b395307898245a652a33d23ca76.jpg&h=1c2c101a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20171201/1251314/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20171201%2F1251314%2F&d=R5uB2q%2F6rUkR92WZqqw0yU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=7116678a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20171201%2F1251314%2F&h=149f93b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20171201/1251314/</a>"},{"pid":"1693a529f96f4899bcc59eb7c7fdc148fa10eca9","tid":485782,"uid":76098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T09:01:17.000Z","msg":"見到膝頭已經j唔落"},{"pid":"70295f7d917e95b00fa556c692773885fa195a74","tid":485782,"uid":23833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T09:02:13.000Z","msg":"50路"},{"pid":"9c463d92dcb54684fe4583334d0f3179516fb573","tid":485782,"uid":22858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"